title: FSX - Newport Photoreal scenery CopenhagenX
description:
Hey, now it must be my turn to share something for FSX on TPB.

Thx to 4X-AXG, papazoff and all of you other guys who have saved me a serious amount of dollars. Now i have bought something and i would like to share it, like you other guys do with your addons. I also have for Atlanta area, will be comming soon in the near future!


This new photo realistic scenery package covers over 3,000 square miles of high resolution night and day textures of Copenhagen, Denmark.

This is an awesome Flight Simulator X add on that will cause a very enjoyable experience as you fly through this remarkable city. This is a very frame rate friendly scenery.
